{"tid":522681,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iMessages 問題","createTime":"2018-01-07T18:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T23:00:21.000Z","uid":89555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dcb748498f2a286016efc45090ba37ba7bcedc5","tid":522681,"uid":89555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:24:25.000Z","msg":"我前一個月轉左cxl之後，部電iphone間唔中就有個類似電信商iMessages 會收費既框框彈出黎要我禁。之前用數xx都無呢個問題，而我又唔係將個iMessages 開開關關，亦都無用過。<br />\n至從換左台之後成日彈框，我覺得好煩就直接閂左iMessages，都仲係會有個框彈出黎。<br />\n有無師兄遇過類似問題？要點樣先可以令佢唔再彈框?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/022416_59ca04d5c2f706fc56f0e30292952223.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F022416_59ca04d5c2f706fc56f0e30292952223.png&h=5585ad04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b086cf003ff77d236956866b2cf01ada338ab37","tid":522681,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"禁ok？"},{"pid":"572a9d22107a7b8f5d382972acb9eb1fde9a0550","tid":522681,"uid":89555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b086cf003ff77d236956866b2cf01ada338ab37","tid":522681,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"禁ok？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:37:44.000Z","msg":"每次都禁ok<br />\n但都係Keep住間唔中彈一次"},{"pid":"9d89e582cf392b6542b740d0a361143e16ebe2f1","tid":522681,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"試曬google嘅方法後<br />\n可以洗機<br />\n唔得可以攞去applestore換機<br />\n利申親身問過"},{"pid":"a8812c5d258c90592b18118a781e242cc2f00b66","tid":522681,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d89e582cf392b6542b740d0a361143e16ebe2f1","tid":522681,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"試曬google嘅方法後<br />\n可以洗機<br />\n唔得可以攞去apple